                </a>
                <a href="/tyo-ja-palkka" class="group block bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-dark-lighter hover:border-primary dark:hover:border-primary transition-colors">
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Työ & Palkka</h3>
